== Compilation instructions

This is the Java version of the daemon. In order to compile, you need:
 * Java Development Kit 6: http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
 * Maven 2 or 3: http://maven.apache.org/


To compile and generate the jar:

  mvn package

To run the daemon directly:

  mvn compile exec:exec


